417
00:23:52,030 --> 00:23:54,863
I had to take
control of something, right?

418
00:23:55,801 --> 00:23:57,268
When to die.

419
00:23:59,304 --> 00:24:02,000
I figured that was
as good as anything.

420
00:24:06,344 --> 00:24:09,780
And that thought
