my pop was crazy,
I never met the man.

483
00:27:45,096 --> 00:27:47,257
With my mom,
it was the drugs.

484
00:27:47,332 --> 00:27:48,799
Any siblings?

485
00:27:49,167 --> 00:27:52,364
