the worst thing you ever did?

493
00:28:30,341 --> 00:28:31,808
You killed four people.

494
00:28:31,876 --> 00:28:34,640
And somehow
making mac and cheese
just the way he wants

495
00:28:34,713 --> 00:28:37,011
kind of loses
its significance.

496
00:28:44,489 --> 00:28:48,152
Oh, no. Now you've left
your entire body in my chair.

497
00:28:48,426 --> 00:28:49,859
What does that mean you want?

498
00:28:49,928 --> 00:28:52,556
I need a segmental
bronchoalveolar lavage.

499
00:28:52,630 --> 00:28:54,723
I take it the CT
with contrast came back?

500
00:28:54,799 --> 00:28:57,597
They're not definitive.
Biopsy would be.

501
00:28:58,069 --> 00:29:00,697
Biopsy would be
invasive and unnecessary.

502
00:29:00,772 --> 00:29:01,932
And definitive.

503
00:29:02,006 --> 00:29:04,600
But you don't want definitive,
you want to hang onto
your delusions

504
00:29:04,676 --> 00:29:05,700
as long as you can.

505
00:29:05,777 --> 00:29:07,745
