to approve the procedure.
Must be a bitch.

507
00:29:11,950 --> 00:29:13,918
The answer is no.
Why?

508
00:29:15,019 --> 00:29:16,646
Because it's me?

509
00:29:17,388 --> 00:29:20,323
I'm over you!
I've jumped on the bandwagon.

510
00:29:20,425 --> 00:29:22,256
And I hate you, okay?

511
00:29:22,727 --> 00:29:24,627
