She's your boss, I get it.

564
00:33:17,195 --> 00:33:19,663
Hitler thought he was doing
the world a favor, too.

565
00:33:19,731 --> 00:33:21,722
Yeah, pretty much
on that same level.

566
00:33:21,799 --> 00:33:24,700
Gandhi didn't march to the sea
