asked him to.

567
00:33:24,769 --> 00:33:27,863
Pol Pot didn't wipe out
the teachers because he
wanted to make friends.

568
00:33:27,939 --> 00:33:30,464
You're not
making friends right now.

569
00:33:31,409 --> 00:33:33,741
I trusted you.
I know.

570
00:33:37,181 --> 00:33:39,706
Wilson's a fool. I'm an idiot.

571
00:33:42,020 --> 00:33:44,614
I had to do
what I thought was right.

572
00:33:45,223 --> 00:33:48,124
It's the only reason
anybody does anything.

573
00:33:50,628 --> 00:33:54,394
Surgery went fine.
They removed almost
a foot of necrotic bowel.

574
00:33:54,465 --> 00:33:56,899
