and taking him into recovery.

575
00:33:56,968 --> 00:33:58,230
I wonder.

576
00:34:00,571 --> 00:34:03,665
I wonder why Clarence killed
that second inmate?

577
00:34:05,610 --> 00:34:08,545
Fine, I'll bite.
What the hell
are you talking about?

578
00:34:08,613 --> 00:34:10,342
Everything we do

