582
00:34:20,625 --> 00:34:23,788
Jealousy.
That gets him sent to prison.

583
00:34:24,796 --> 00:34:27,526
Where he kills
inmate number one. Why?

584
00:34:28,199 --> 00:34:30,099
Guy attacked him first.

585
00:34:30,701 --> 00:34:31,929
Revenge.

586
00:34:32,003 --> 00:34:34,733
Who'd he kill after that?
Prison guard.

587
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:38,034
Who had a file
full of abuse complaints.

588
00:34:38,109 --> 00:34:40,475
Probably been kicking
Clarence's ass for months.

589
00:34:40,545 --> 00:34:42,877
Clarence is just ridding
the world of bad seeds.

590
00:34:42,947 --> 00:34:44,744
We'll call that one
retribution.

591
00:34:46,250 --> 00:34:48,616
Then he kills
inmate number two.

592
00:34:50,054 --> 00:34:51,646
Anybody know why?

593
00:34:52,457 --> 00:34:53,481
Uh-uh.

594
00:34:53,558 --> 00:34:55,219
It's not in there.

595
00:35:01,099 --> 00:35:03,567
CLARENCE: All of a sudden,
I gotta have a reason?

596
00:35:03,634 --> 00:35:06,967
It's an anomaly.
Doctors love anomalies.

597
00:35:07,939 --> 00:35:11,431
Dark spot on an x-ray,
bright spot on an MRl.

598
00:35:12,076 --> 00:35:13,941
Killing that second inmate

599
00:35:14,011 --> 00:35:18,141
