inks with heavy metals.

659
00:38:56,734 --> 00:38:58,634
The MRl is basically
a giant magnet,

660
00:38:58,703 --> 00:39:01,763
suck those metallic inks
right out of your skin.

661
00:39:13,084 --> 00:39:14,381
(GROANlNG)

662
00:39:16,420 --> 00:39:17,785
(SCREAMlNG)

663
00:39:26,130 --> 00:39:27,722
Stop squirming.

664
00:39:28,232 --> 00:39:30,359
Don't make us do this again.

665
00:39:32,536 --> 00:39:33,901
Big baby.

666
00:39:34,538 --> 00:39:36,529
Still don't see anything.

667
00:39:37,842 --> 00:39:38,866
(CLARENCE GROANlNG)

668
00:39:38,943 --> 00:39:40,342
CLARENCE: Turn it off!

669
00:39:41,045 --> 00:39:42,535
There's Waldo.

670
00:39:43,781 --> 00:39:45,510
Found it, Clarence.

671
00:39:45,649 --> 00:39:47,048
Turn it off!

672
00:39:47,284 --> 00:39:49,149
Turn this damn thing off!

673
00:39:49,220 --> 00:39:52,212
Keep him in there
until you guys see it, too.

674
00:39:52,723 --> 00:39:54,281
Son of a bitch.

675
00:40:03,134 --> 00:40:06,228
Looks like they got
the pheo out successfully.

676
00:40:07,571 --> 00:40:09,061
So, what now?

677
00:40:09,874 --> 00:40:12,069
Clarence goes back
to death row.

678
00:40:12,143 --> 00:40:13,667
Just like that?

679
00:40:14,111 --> 00:40:15,476
He's cured.

680
00:40:16,747 --> 00:40:19,113
That tumor caused
random shots of adrenalin,

681
00:40:19,183 --> 00:40:22,641
which obviously led
to the rage attacks that
made him become a murderer

682
00:40:22,720 --> 00:40:24,278
in the first place.

683
00:40:24,388 --> 00:40:25,980
My God, you're right!

684
00:40:26,056 --> 00:40:28,581
